SRGAN Image Super-Resolution

Project Abstract

This project implements a Super-Resolution Generative Adversarial Network (SRGAN) for single image super-resolution. The system utilizes ONNX Runtime for cross-platform deployment and demonstrates real-time image enhancement from 128×128 to 512×512 resolution (4× upscaling factor).

Framework:
ONNX Runtime, Next.js, Tensorflow
